net.cloud.gfx.constants

Class FontConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.gfx.constants.FontConstants

  • public class FontConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants that pair with usage of the Font object throughout the application. For example, contains constants to base text size on. For various Font objects themselves, refer to the Fonts class.
    See Also:
    Fonts
